      <title>加纳在债权人协议草案后接近国际货币基金组织的 3.6 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/ghana-to-win-bilateral-debt-pact-unlocking-360-million-from-imf</link>
